				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$N=2$$\end{document}N=2, noting that here only stationary patterns can form. For \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
